ExpSyntax.val: MlsTrans('Date To must less than or equal Posting Date')

SQL_STMT_U.val: select i.docentry,objtype,i.agentname,i.totalcost, i.agentcode from ( select docentry,agentname,sum(opencost) totalcost,agentcode from ipf2 (nolock) where not agentcode is null and opencost>0 and (agentcode=':1' or ':1' is null or ':1' ='') group by docentry,agentname,agentcode ) i , OIPF o (nolock) where i.docentry=o.docentry and (o.DocDate between :4 and ':5') and o.DocDate <= ':3' and (U_IDU_kode_PT=':2' or ':2' is null or ':2' ='') and o.docstatus = 'O' and o.CANCELED = 'N' and o.DocCur = :6
